<hymn_number>221</hymn_number>
<title>Lalpa Chenna Gamnuom</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Jordan luipanga ka din chun,
 Ka thil Lalpa chenna gam nuom;
 Kanaan gam leh ka kumsawt mun ding chu,
 Thangvan gam nuom pielgal ahi.

[V2]
 Thih nung leh chawl ingka,
 Isu kawm thangvan gam nuomah;
 Belam No chawihatna'n zaila hawih sang ting,
 Kipakna pak hawih chu lun zing tana.

[V3]
 2. Zie gam nuom lam chu ka thilin,
 Kumsawt vak chun ka lung a kuoi;
 Kah leh lungkham mauna beihna gam chu,
 Tun ka nuom hi thangvan gam chu.

[V4]
 3. Bangtik leh kei le ka tung dem,
 Hukdam chate nawp lenna mun?
 Ei lungsiet Lalpa vanga ka tun tieng,
 Gimna mun lei hi ngai puong ie.

[V5]
 4. Zie gam nuom lam chu ka thilin,
 Ka lunggil kipahnan a dim;
 Lungkham pulthuok leh kahna beihna mun,
 Kipahna zailan a dim hi.</lyrics>
</song>